robert sarver  wikipedia robert sarver from wikipedia the free encyclopedia jump to navigation search robert sarver sarver  born  age – nationality united states occupation businessman real estate investor known for owner of phoenix suns owner of rcd mallorca president of western alliance bancorporation owner of southwest value partners net worth us million  spouses penny sanders children max sarver jake sarver zach sarver parents irene and jack sarver contents  early life and education  career  phoenix suns  rangers  rcd mallorca  personal life  references early life and educationedit sarver was born to a jewish family in tucson the son of irene and jack sarver his father was a prominent tucson businessman banker and hotel developer the elder sarver built the aztec inn the plaza international hotel now an aloft hotel at speedway and campbell in tucson in the early s built and operated the tucson area howard johnsons locations and headed a local savings and loan jack sarver died of a heart attack in  robert sarver would eventually donate to his alma mater the university of arizona funds to its heart research center which in  was renamed the sarver heart center in honor of his father at age  he went to work for his fathers company american savings and loan sarver is a  graduate of sabino high school in tucson and a  graduate of the university of arizona with a bachelors degree in business administration in  sarver became a certified public accountant careeredit in  sarver founded the national bank of tucson which he expanded statewide and change the name to the national bank of arizona in  he cofounded the real estate company southwest value partners with millard seldin in  he sold the national bank of arizona then the largest independent bank in the state to zions bancorporation in  southwest value partners purchased the emerald plaza in san diego in  he acquired grossmont bank one of san diegos largest community banks grossmont was also sold to zions bancorporation in  in  his jointly owned real estate firm southwest value partners sold the emerald plaza and two other san diego office buildings to santa ana real estate firm triple net properties for  million in  he led zions bancorporations acquisition of sumitomo bank of california in  he became chairman president and ceo of western alliance bancorporation phoenix sunsedit a lifelong sports fan sarvers quest to purchase an nba team began with a conversation with university of arizona basketball coach lute olson olson referred sarver to steve kerr a former player at arizona and a year nba veteran to assist him in buying an nba franchise in  he purchased the suns for a record  million in october  robert sarver was also ranked as the worst owner in the nba by espn rangersedit on the th january  robert sarver offered £ million for control of scottish football side rangers football club having previously had a bid of £ million turned down a couple of weeks earlier the second offer was also rejected and sarver ended his pursuit to buy rangers rcd mallorcaedit on the th january  robert sarver bought rcd mallorca a spanish second division football team for € personal lifeedit in  he married penny sanders a kansas city missouri native they have three sons max b  jake b  and zach b  they live in paradise valley arizona sarver sits on the board of trustees of the sarver heart center tucson which he helped build in memory of his late father who was among the first in an experimental group to undergo bypass surgery the sarver center is affiliated with the university of arizona and houses over  physicians and researchers dedicated to fight heart disease sarver plays golf tennis and volleyball and enjoys going to california in his spare timecitation needed referencesedit  arizona jewish post wandering jews former tucsonans thrive in new locales – robert sarver september    arizona daily star article on the former plaza international hotel built by robert sarvers father  sarver heart center